{"name":"Self-Destructive Magic","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/fire/explosion-flame-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your race was born from the war experiments of humans: they infused heavy doses of elemental magic to create living weapons. Early specimens were highly unstable, with strong powers but ended up dying in excruciating torment. You, like your ancestors, put your own physical integrity at risk to channel your magical power.</p><p>You gain the following benefits:</p><p>• Your CON score increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• As a bonus action, you can consume a number of hit dice to gain a spell slot of a level equal to the number of hit dice spent, up to a maximum equal to your proficiency bonus. You also roll the corresponding hit dice and reduce your maximum HP by the result you get. For example, if you are a 5th-level fighter, you can consume up to 3 life dice at a time and recover up to a 3rd-level spell slot, after which you roll 1d10 for the level of the recovered spell slot and reduce your maximum HP by the total gained. This reduction in maximum HP cannot be reduced or cancelled by any source and lasts until you complete a long rest.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"iRdW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Half Elementals","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"label":"Constitution Increase","icon":"icons/magic/fire/explosion-flame-blue.webp","origin":"Item.PSehNWs5heMWlbnG","duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"comba