{"name":"Mighty Arms","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/hand-grip-staff-yellow-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You are dedicated to improving your physique, being able to lift and throw opponents with ease.</p><p>You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your STR score increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency in STR (Athletics), or expertise if you already possessed proficiency.</p></li><li><p>As an attack action, you can throw a target that is grabbed by you. You cannot cast creatures that are two size categories or larger than you. If you are able to make multiple attacks through the attack action, this replaces one of them. You make a STR (Athletic) check against a STR (Athletic) check of the target. The target is no longer grabbed by you (regardless of the result). If successful, you throw the target into a space within 6 m (20 ft.) of you and the target falls prone suffering 1d6 + your STR mod. bludgeoning damage. If the space is occupied by a creature, it must make a DEX save with DC equal to 8 + your competence bonus + your STR mod.. If it fails, it takes damage like the target and falls prone. The primary target, in this case, lands in a space of your choice within 5 ft (1.5 m) of the secondary target and suffers the normal effects of the throw.</p></li></ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"iRdW","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":"target that is grabbed by you. You cannot cast creatures that are two size  categories or larger than you."},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"touch","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"abil","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6 + @mod","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","sa