{"name":"Night's Emissary","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/light/light-lantern-lit-white.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Darkness is the domain of vampires and their spawn. You have neared vampire skills, becoming an experienced and stealthy hunter of the night. You gain the following benefits:</p><p>• Your darkvision increases by 60 ft (18 m).</p><p>• You can transform into a @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.monsters.qav2dvMIUiMQCCsy]{bat}, a @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.monsters.yawTeS8u2FCfzzZH]{wolf}, or a @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.monsters.pozQUPTnLZW8epox]{rat}. This ability follows the rules of the druid’s Wild Form, but it does not count in the total number of uses of this ability if you have druid levels, it lasts a maximum of 1 hour, and you do not have to meet certain levels to select one of these creatures. You can use this ability twice, and you recover the spent uses when you complete a long rest.</p><p>• You learn the Suggestion spell. You can cast it without spending spell slots once this way, and you cannot cast it again until you complete a long rest. You can also cast it using spell slots of an appropriate level. INT, WIS or CHA is your spellcasting characteristic for this spell when you cast it with this ability (you determine this when you choose this talent).</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"iRdW","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"2","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"vampires","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"kg10vII5VzQknnnc":3},"flags":{"magicite